# Social Media Checklist for College Students

# Do's

- Think before you post anything online  
- Use strong passwords and enable 2FA  
- Respect others and communicate politely  
- Verify information before sharing  
- Keep your personal information private  

---

#  Don'ts

- Do not share OTPs or sensitive data  
- Do not post offensive or harmful content  
- Avoid clicking on unknown or suspicious links  
- Do not overshare personal life publicly  
- Avoid spreading fake news or rumors  
